{"tid":2269330,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"銀礦灣Staycation群組累計五人中招","createTime":"2020-11-03T11:56:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-03T11:56:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"095dd9980e99af26e766ac617cead7b27d816be1","tid":2269330,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T11:56:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201103/C5IIFGNJLVDLPDPLWDBJY5JH74/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201103%2FC5IIFGNJLVDLPDPLWDBJY5JH74%2F&d=AZYGjn5ll7vy7cK20AVbo8kuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=0b9b30c5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201103%2FC5IIFGNJLVDLPDPLWDBJY5JH74%2F&h=95560ef0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201103/C5IIFGNJLVDLPDPLWDBJY5JH74/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n銀礦灣Staycation群組累計五人中招<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】本港昨新增六宗確診，包括三宗輸入及三宗來自銀礦灣海景渡假樂園Staycation群組。據悉，該群組同時新增兩宗初步確診個案，即該群組至今有五人確診及初步確診。有線新聞引述消息指，該群組最先發病的第5332號26歲女子，與部份朋友在銀礦灣度假後，意猶未盡，再返家繼續卡拉OK及打麻雀盡興。食衞局長陳肇始警告，若市民不自律，政府不排除會收緊社交距離措施。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：大圍鳳樓 東方泛達接客  妓女確診 超級電腦追蹤百嫖客<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/2vkzfJsxi0cdWKYothYG3H4uDVg=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XIUMJ2EAVNHXHLVNWUBMKBRKY4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F2vkzfJsxi0cdWKYothYG3H4uDVg%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXIUMJ2EAVNHXHLVNWUBMKBRKY4.jpg&h=b56f9d70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■銀礦灣海景渡假樂園Staycation群組至今有五人確診及初步確診。<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心指，第5332號患者屬本地源頭不明個案。她10月25至27日曾與七名友人入住梅窩銀礦灣海景渡假樂園，。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/q3oRq3JILCZhLT2Vs96zlO5fyuA=/1527x2315/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/D6PCMLJTG5AGJH6FKPM3WX5OAI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fq3oRq3JILCZhLT2Vs96zlO5fyuA%3D%2F1527x2315%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FD6PCMLJTG5AGJH6FKPM3WX5OAI.gif&h=ef3aa26f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n傳播鏈涉唱K打麻雀<br />\n<br />\n有線新聞昨引述消息，披露患者的接觸過程，指第5332號及第5336號與部份朋友於10月27日完結梅窩三日兩夜度假後，意猶未盡，再到第5332號位於圍頭村寓所卡拉OK及打麻雀聚會，該聚會尚有並無參與梅窩度假的第5337號15歲男童及一名26歲男子，即合共九人，這名參與圍頭村聚會的26歲男子及另一名人士昨亦初步確診。報道又指，第5332號等八人在梅窩度假期間，先後去過德仔記、幾好餐廳及順興海鮮等用膳。<br />\n<br />\n政府社交距離措施本周四屆滿，陳肇始昨在電台節目指出，留。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n港大感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良在同一電台目上指，。。。。。。。。。。口罩等有關，呼籲市民盡量減少聚集。"}]}